//
// A `kind: ui` plugin (web-portal, CLI, Slack bot, VS Code extension) is an
// experience surface. The platform's multi-UI story (overview.md / Phase 5) is
// "each UI is a separate ui plugin" — so this contract is deliberately thin: a
// UI plugin mostly CONSUMES the API gateway like any other client. What the core
